    # det "We've talked to the two people he lived with - Lisa and Suzy."
    det "Já falámos com as duas pessoas com quem ele vivia — a Lisa e a Suzy."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez0.rpy:69
translate portuguese questionsfirst_a76cc077:

    # pc "That's all?"
    pc "É tudo?"

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez0.rpy:70
translate portuguese questionsfirst_07673981:

    # det "From my notes, you are the only remaining family member, and you were out of the country."
    det "Pelas minhas notas, és o único familiar que resta, e estavas fora do país."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez0.rpy:71
translate portuguese questionsfirst_249eced2:

    # det "Previous wife died of cancer, both parents died of natural causes, no siblings."
    det "A ex-mulher morreu de cancro, ambos os pais morreram de causas naturais, não tem irmãos."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez0.rpy:72
translate portuguese questionsfirst_8ba569c2:

    # det "And it seems as if your father did not have very many friends. By all accounts he spent most of his time in the basement."
    det "E parece que o teu pai não tinha muitos amigos. Ao que tudo indica, passava a maior parte do tempo na cave."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez0.rpy:74
