translate portuguese questionsfirst_499a2c32:

    # pc "It involves engineering on a quantum level. So, he wasn't a computer programmer, he was a scientist."
    pc "Envolve engenharia a nível quântico. Então, ele não era programador de computadores, era cientista."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez0.rpy:87
translate portuguese questionsfirst_c1c65336:

    # det "Okay, but he worked for PQ Technologies, right?"
    det "Está bem, mas ele trabalhava para a PQ Technologies, certo?"

