translate portuguese questionsfirst_e2d71efb:

    # pc "Not really, no. Quantum engineering is all I know. He never really talked about his work."
    pc "Na verdade, não. Engenharia quântica é tudo o que sei. Ele nunca falava realmente sobre o seu trabalho."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez0.rpy:95
translate portuguese questionsfirst_eb4656fe:

    # det "I see. Well, I talked to his supervisor and from what I can tell, the two did not really have a relationship."
    det "Entendo. Bem, falei com o supervisor dele e, pelo que percebi, os dois não tinham realmente uma relação."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez0.rpy:96
translate portuguese questionsfirst_6c7e47a3:

    # det "Your father sent his work in weekly and the company paid his salary."
    det "O seu pai enviava o trabalho semanalmente e a empresa pagava-lhe o salário."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez0.rpy:97
translate portuguese questionsfirst_77d22bd2:

    # det "Everything was conducted through e-mail and there was no real contact."
    det "Tudo era feito por e-mail e não havia contacto real."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez0.rpy:102
translate portuguese questionsfirst_3eb51a74:

    # det "Our investigators looked through his car, which seems like it hadn't been driven in a long time."
