    # det "We did a walk-through of the house and didn't see anything suspicious."
    det "Fizemos uma inspeção à casa e não vimos nada de suspeito."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez0.rpy:105
translate portuguese questionsfirst_9c61ea6b:

    # det "We went into the basement and looked through his equipment, but it seemed to all be work-related stuff down there."
    det "Fomos à cave e revistámos o equipamento dele, mas parecia que lá em baixo só havia coisas relacionadas com o trabalho."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez0.rpy:106
