    # det "Our techs tried to gain access to his computer, but everything was password protected and encrypted."
    det "Os nossos técnicos tentaram aceder ao computador dele, mas tudo estava protegido por palavra-passe e encriptado."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez0.rpy:107
translate portuguese questionsfirst_a3576891:

    # det "From our investigation, it did not seem there were any clues to be gained by searching the house further."
    det "Pela nossa investigação, não parecia haver pistas a obter com uma busca mais aprofundada à casa."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez0.rpy:112
translate portuguese questionsfirst_6f494b23:

    # "She looks up at me with compassionate eyes."
    "Ela olha para mim com olhos compassivos."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez0.rpy:113
translate portuguese questionsfirst_cb6742cd:

    # det "Oh no, I don't think so."
    det "Oh não, acho que não."

