translate portuguese questionsfirst_f3918cf6:

    # pc "I wouldn't say I was angry. We had some arguments before I left. It was all just teenage bullshit."
    pc "Não diria que estava zangado. Tivemos algumas discussões antes de eu partir. Era tudo apenas tretas de adolescentes."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez0.rpy:160
translate portuguese questionsfirst_1575bf56:

    # pc "I love my dad and I very much want to find him."
    pc "Adoro o meu pai e quero muito encontrá-lo."

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez0.rpy:161
